WEBVTT

00:00.062 --> 00:03.950
_

00:22.440 --> 00:24.660
I'm not asking you to
give me the lease for free.

00:24.662 --> 00:27.464
I'm telling you to overcharge
me on the rest of the building

00:27.466 --> 00:30.233
and then look the other way
for the rent on that space.

00:30.235 --> 00:34.003
Oh, you can't or you won't?

00:34.005 --> 00:36.506
Ashley, I got this. Why
don't you take a long lunch?

00:36.508 --> 00:38.340
- Okay.
- Because if you can't, Alan,

00:38.342 --> 00:40.075
I got to talk to the person who can.

00:40.077 --> 00:42.911
And if you won't, well, let's
talk about why you won't.

00:42.913 --> 00:46.014
I always say that everything
happens for a reason.

00:46.016 --> 00:48.484
Now, I have something I have to get to,

00:48.486 --> 00:51.720
so I have exactly five more
minutes to spend on this,

00:51.722 --> 00:54.456
but just so we're clear,
at the end of this call,

00:54.458 --> 00:57.126
we will either have a deal

00:57.128 --> 00:59.861
or we will never have a deal.

01:02.015 --> 01:04.933
No, no, no! No, today is the day!

01:04.935 --> 01:06.368
I can't be in this marriage anymore,

01:06.370 --> 01:07.642
and I want to be with you.

01:07.645 --> 01:09.845
Now, in exactly 5 hours, 12 minutes,

01:09.848 --> 01:11.181
Katherine's gonna come home.

01:11.184 --> 01:14.364
She's gonna want to get
takeout Indian food again.

01:14.367 --> 01:15.910
My people are from Milwaukee.

01:15.912 --> 01:17.912
We weren't bred to
eat that much vindaloo.

01:21.351 --> 01:23.284
I don't know what I'm gonna tell Theo.

01:23.286 --> 01:25.853
Maybe that Daddy needs to be happy.

01:25.855 --> 01:28.489
- Eddie?
- Damn it.

01:28.491 --> 01:30.258
I forgot my briefcase.

01:30.260 --> 01:31.759
Didn't you notice I left it?

01:31.761 --> 01:33.961
Ah. Hey, you!

01:33.963 --> 01:35.396
Great.

01:35.398 --> 01:37.198
Now I lost an hour out of my day.

01:37.200 --> 01:38.688
Now I don't have time to pick up Theo.

01:38.690 --> 01:39.933
Uh, you got him, right?

01:39.935 --> 01:42.436
Oh. Actually, I was gonna
teach a guitar lesson at noon.

01:42.438 --> 01:44.705
Unbelievable. She didn't file
the motion, like I told her to.

01:44.707 --> 01:46.840
Why is everyone an idiot?

01:46.842 --> 01:49.243
Okay, so, uh, you got Theo?

01:49.245 --> 01:51.312
- Yeah.
- Okay.

01:51.314 --> 01:52.513
See you tonight.

02:13.002 --> 02:14.334
Sorry to keep you waiting, Gary.

02:14.336 --> 02:16.503
Just wanted to review your X-ray.

02:16.505 --> 02:18.345
It's in line with what I was expecting.

02:18.348 --> 02:20.607
Wow, Doc. The suspense is killing me.

02:21.711 --> 02:22.910
Is anything else killing me?

02:22.912 --> 02:25.512
The fact is...

02:25.514 --> 02:26.747
Dr. Martin.

02:26.749 --> 02:28.682
No, I was very clear...

02:28.684 --> 02:30.584
Balsamic vinaigrette.

02:30.586 --> 02:32.485
Yes, they do. I get salad
there three days a week.

02:32.487 --> 02:34.154
It's right next to the edamame.

02:34.156 --> 02:35.622
Are you looking at the edamame?

02:35.624 --> 02:37.891
That brownish liquid next
to the edamame is called...

02:37.893 --> 02:38.959
Sorry.

02:38.961 --> 02:40.427
I don't mean to interrupt

02:40.429 --> 02:42.862
what sounds like a super
important salad conversation.

02:42.865 --> 02:45.098
I just have one quick question.

02:45.100 --> 02:47.633
Is my cancer back?

02:47.636 --> 02:50.770
And so more than three
years after the crisis began,

02:50.773 --> 02:53.973
the class-action lawsuit
is once again making

02:53.975 --> 02:56.676
water in Flint,
Michigan, front-page news.

03:24.506 --> 03:26.873
...were aware of the contamination.

03:26.875 --> 03:29.809
For months, Flint
reside were unaware that

03:29.811 --> 03:33.712
water from their own faucet
was silently killing them.

03:33.714 --> 03:36.715
When the defendants became
aware of the crisis...

03:47.399 --> 03:50.133
...water crisis in
Flint as a wake-up call.

03:55.770 --> 03:56.936
What?!

03:56.938 --> 03:58.404
You're not gonna believe this.

04:27.767 --> 04:30.294
Jon killed himself.

04:37.777 --> 04:42.947
